title: ENS workshop 2021 Autumn community voting
body:
After watching the project pitch at the ENS workshop, please vote for your favourite project. The winning project wins $1000 worth of ETH/Stable coin and you will get the community voter POAP badge.

- [YouTube live link](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ozRLXQwJmA)
- [The project detail](https://discuss.ens.domains/t/ens-workshop-2021-autumn-community-show-tell/781)
